  "body": "<p>It's truly pregnancy brain when you turn to a friend and tell them you are stuck on an assignment for scrapbooking milestones. Without skipping a beat, she simply said, “how about your pregnancy?”. And then we went on to giggle about the whole thing. Here is how my Milestones layout came together. I started off with putting down a thin layer of gesso using a foam brush from side to side. After drying, I added some splatters.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766687113-1T2ETW8OXXJYZ6TP8HWS/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I placed the photos down (without adhering them) for planning the rest of the page.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766704903-HDXNUY2CF1WB0KR7CSMQ/2b-DSC_0029-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2c-DSC_0030-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766740561-505GD4FQY8FXC1DXGENP/2c-DSC_0030-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"2j-DSC_0040-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766759791-RDXLEJAPZGWEYO92L8LE/2j-DSC_0040-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"2d-DSC_0031-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766740188-8D76G847KCPWFLWV4XH8/2d-DSC_0031-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2e-DSC_0032-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766740545-XEZC0PCNNBSDTJ1ILB0Z/2e-DSC_0032-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2f-DSC_0035-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766741419-VD4TLSBGY5VVYH1E474J/2f-DSC_0035-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2g-DSC_0036-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766740967-5LP92LXUX8ZZEIFKJFNW/2g-DSC_0036-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2h-DSC_0038-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766741427-5DYXQSDB8J54X4TEGAB1/2h-DSC_0038-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2i-DSC_0039-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766741807-LXWDW21FT059KYOENC03/2i-DSC_0039-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Final touch was some chevron stitching using our <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139091-capture-yes-please-amy-tangerine-embroidery-stencil-kit/%3Fsource_type%3DLAY%26source_id%3D1919612\">Capture embroidery stencil kit</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"2k-hello-bump2-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766801608-55OLOAYOTXT3QYY465IR/2k-hello-bump2-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"2l-hello-bump.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599766802761-RQ7ELAFOMM6UE0KMO5P9/2l-hello-bump.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1919612-hello-bump-milestones/\">Hello Bump</a> | Copyright Two Peas In A BucketComplete supply list can be found at <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1919612-hello-bump-milestones/\">Two Peas In A Bucket</a>.</p>"
